Village of WhistleberryvillagenM0none12764493680searchvar0.8593404*06*****03*Named after the unique grey wildberries which grow around the village, Whistleberry might be the place for you if you are looking for good food, good stores and good rest. The guards are very competent although an extremely small amount of criminality still remains; this can be explained by the fact that this village is an ancient military camp where elite soldiers were sent to train.